{"title":"fix: Adjust stress container memory usage to match declared limit","body":"## Root Cause
The Deployment/vigil-app:mem-load container had a memory limit mismatch. The stress command attempted to allocate 50M (approximately 47.68Mi) while the declared memory limit was only 32Mi. This caused container failures as the container tried to exceed its allocated memory.

## Evidence
