   volumes:\n        - name: nginx-config-template\n          configMap:\n            name: vigil-app-nginx-config","discovered_sysctl_key":null}

## Fix
Updated the stress container command from `["stress", "--vm", "1", "--vm-bytes", "50M", "--vm-keep"]` to `["stress", "--vm", "1", "--vm-bytes", "32M", "--vm-keep"]` to ensure the container operates within its declared 32Mi memory limit."}
